high_descs: Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the chair then take a step to your left and walk just past the chair then turn right and walk to the table to the left of the chair at the head of the table where the newspaper is.
Pick up the newspaper that's in front of you.

Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the couch then turn right and walk to the fireplace then turn left and walk to the coffee table then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the ottoman.
Put the newspaper on the right edge of the ottoman near the bottom right corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a newspaper on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the stairs, then hang a left and walk across the room to the far side of the large wooden table.
Pick up the newspaper off of the large wooden table.
Make your way to the purple chair with the foot stool in front of it.
Put the newspaper on the right side of the foot stool.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper to a foot stool.

high_descs: Turn around and move across the room, and face the table on the right.
Pick up the newspaper from the left corner.
Carry the newspaper and turn to the left. Turn right to go in the next room. Move forward past the furniture and then left to see the ottoman and chair.
Place the newspaper on the ottoman, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper to the ottoman.
